{"tid":1592470,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[不完美待改善] 家長點睇近日嘅時代革命","createTime":"2019-09-24T15:34:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-25T00:56:29.000Z","uid":78790,"like":39,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"5839efc893af1d33cdbf8acb2b480081117e5ae5","tid":1592470,"uid":78790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:34:11.000Z","msg":"我幫人開post，重點請到文末睇顏色字<br />\n<br />\n同事係30中，淺黃，中低層前線管理人員<br />\n有兩個幼稚園同小學嘅小朋友<br />\n<br />\n佢好支持呢場運動，深信係救到小朋友嘅將來<br />\n但有家庭同工作負擔，極少參與<br />\n才疏學淺，唔識詳解件事比小朋友聽<br />\n<br />\n今日食飯佢比小朋友相我睇<br />\n係佢近日帶小朋友去APM食野順便行街<br />\n去完APM就有幾樣野不解<br />\n想手足們諗下計幫下佢同各位家長<br />\n<br />\n1) 係商場叫口號可以爭取到乜野<br />\n佢無覺得擾民，可能佢唔係感受咁深所以唔明。<br />\n我同佢講，呢個係一種打氣活動，大家聚埋一齊唱歌叫口號，參與者會感覺到仲有人一齊，齊上齊落。佢明白左。如果有手足有更好解釋，請指教。<br />\n<br />\n2) 在場人士有人呼籲唔好影相<br />\na) 大家都有自由用手提電話，同小朋友出街影下可愛相在所難免。佢唔係嘉年華心態地參與運動，只係路過。<br />\n在場人士如果怕被清算，為左保護自己係咪都應該戴返個口罩。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>點解仲有人會連口罩都無個，要全世界就佢地保護佢地?</strong> </span><br />\n<br />\nb) 有一把聲呼籲&quot;唔好影相呀唔該&quot;，隨即有一位blackbloc手足衝出黎:&quot;<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>我屌你老母影乜撚野相呀</strong></span>&quot;<br />\n佢作為一個家長，唔係對粗口潔癖，但帶住小朋友果陣，會比人問:<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>&quot;個哥哥點解咁惡嘅?&quot; &quot;媽咪唔係話佢地唔係壞人咩?&quot;</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>各位手足係呢啲和理非場合可唔可以克制返少少?</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n3) 佢真係唔識點同小朋友解釋件事嘅來龍去脈，小朋友得七歲，<span style=\"color: red;\">請問有冇適合小朋友睇嘅文宣 / 材料(例如: 漫畫)</span>?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光 復 香 港<br />\n時 代 革 命</span></span>"},{"pid":"248d11f519fee1f1f727c65d5817e4d999d487e2","tid":1592470,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:34:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biFbOWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiFbOWs.png&h=404dfcfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【929行動】大家好，我地係Chinazi。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590320\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590320</a>"},{"pid":"dcf4ec25d6b32de25cad2843a5b47a1cf70fa5bf","tid":1592470,"uid":78790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:34:35.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"832de2117aad94831353bfa33f77965f4305ee7a","tid":1592470,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:36:00.000Z","msg":"［請幫推行動post］今星期四：和你塞 美心MX<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1590453\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1590453</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O4KHbAX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO4KHbAX.jpg&h=3211b048&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"32a27768dded29137b95f21a9d284c5703066fb9","tid":1592470,"uid":78790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:36:04.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"90c78d7ba7a46218002bd06734b05ef3f0c9da85","tid":1592470,"uid":235465,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:36:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />話要有禮貌 講左幾個月又變翻咁"},{"pid":"a97aeb9cabd1fc6003eb47b61d73b88183abbcde","tid":1592470,"uid":78790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"90c78d7ba7a46218002bd06734b05ef3f0c9da85","tid":1592470,"uid":235465,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:36:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />話要有禮貌 講左幾個月又變翻咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:38:13.000Z","msg":"我深信只要出得黎基本配備返個口罩<br />\n就唔會有人呼籲唔好影相<br />\n亦唔會有手足靠兇嘅方法叫人唔好影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6e1b05877868f7b290ec21a946f6665ac3d134b","tid":1592470,"uid":78790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:39:20.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"1e6ac4f69b9f6e847c3c845dd9543e5e6aeb5dd7","tid":1592470,"uid":78790,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T15:43:39.000Z","msg":"721之後我睇到何妖墳頭嘅post<br />\n我同佢講，何君琴晚率眾妖害人<br />\n如果有咩事報應係佢身上，我地